originalSql:
SELECT 
    CONCAT(s.s_name, ' (', r.r_name, ')') AS supplier_info,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ps.ps_partkey) AS total_parts_supplied,
    SUM(ps.ps_availqty) AS total_available_quantity,
    AVG(p.p_retailprice) AS average_part_price,
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT p.p_name, ', ') AS part_names
FROM 
    supplier s
JOIN 
    partsupp ps ON s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey
JOIN 
    part p ON ps.ps_partkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN 
    nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN 
    region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
WHERE 
    p.p_size > 10 AND 
    s.s_acctbal > (SELECT AVG(s_acctbal) FROM supplier)
GROUP BY 
    supplier_info
ORDER BY 
    total_parts_supplied DESC

FROM (SELECT CONCAT("supplier0"."s_name", ' (', "region"."r_name", ')') AS "FD_D_f0", ANY_VALUE(CONCAT("supplier0"."s_name", ' (', "region"."r_name", ')')) AS "SUPPLIER_INFO", COUNT(DISTINCT "partsupp"."ps_partkey") AS "TOTAL_PARTS_SUPPLIED", SUM("partsupp"."ps_availqty") AS "TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY", AVG("t0"."p_retailprice") AS "AVERAGE_PART_PRICE", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "t0"."p_name", ', ') AS "PART_NAMES"
FROM (SELECT AVG("s_acctbal") AS "EXPR$0"
FROM "supplier") AS "t"
INNER JOIN ("region" INNER JOIN "nation" ON "region"."r_regionkey" = "nation"."n_regionkey" INNER JOIN "supplier" AS "supplier0" ON "nation"."n_nationkey" = "supplier0"."s_nationkey") ON "t"."EXPR$0" < "supplier0"."s_acctbal"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "part"
WHERE "p_size" > 10) AS "t0" INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "t0"."p_partkey" = "partsupp"."ps_partkey") ON "supplier0"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey"
GROUP BY CONCAT("supplier0"."s_name", ' (', "region"."r_name", ')')
ORDER BY 3 DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t3"

SELECT COALESCE("ps_partkey", "ps_partkey") AS "ps_partkey", "ps_suppkey", "ps_availqty", "ps_supplycost", "ps_comment"
FROM "partsupp"

SELECT COALESCE("t4"."SUPPLIER_INFO", "t4"."SUPPLIER_INFO") AS "SUPPLIER_INFO", "t4"."TOTAL_PARTS_SUPPLIED", "t4"."TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY", "t4"."AVERAGE_PART_PRICE", "t4"."PART_NAMES"
FROM (SELECT CONCAT("supplier0"."s_name", ' (', "region"."r_name", ')') AS "FD_D_f0", MIN(CONCAT("supplier0"."s_name", ' (', "region"."r_name", ')')) AS "SUPPLIER_INFO", COUNT(DISTINCT "s1"."ps_partkey") AS "TOTAL_PARTS_SUPPLIED", SUM("s1"."ps_availqty") AS "TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY", AVG("t1"."p_retailprice") AS "AVERAGE_PART_PRICE", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "t1"."p_name", ', ') AS "PART_NAMES"
FROM (SELECT AVG("s_acctbal") AS "EXPR$0"
FROM "supplier") AS "t0"
INNER JOIN ("region" INNER JOIN "nation" ON "region"."r_regionkey" = "nation"."n_regionkey" INNER JOIN "supplier" AS "supplier0" ON "nation"."n_nationkey" = "supplier0"."s_nationkey") ON "t0"."EXPR$0" < "supplier0"."s_acctbal"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "part"
WHERE "p_size" > 10) AS "t1" INNER JOIN "s1" ON "t1"."p_partkey" = "s1"."ps_partkey") ON "supplier0"."s_suppkey" = "s1"."ps_suppkey"
GROUP BY CONCAT("supplier0"."s_name", ' (', "region"."r_name", ')')
ORDER BY 3 DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t4"
